    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Yes. The fact that not using pylab works is an accident that's OS and backend dependent and can't be relied upon.  The only officially supported way of using matplotlib interactively with possibly multiple plots and a fully non-blocking window is to use --pylab or %pylab.\n\nClosing as not a bug.\n"
